{"TopicId":186890,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"\u0026#039;The Martian\u0026#039; easter egg on Duna","CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Dressian Exploder","CreatedById":191542,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, basically, an easter egg on Duna that\u0027d be referencing\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EThe Martian\u003C/em\u003E in some way. Comment what you think!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIdeas for the easter egg I\u0027ve had so far:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nMAV base\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHab somewhere on the ground\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe rover, complete with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E in the cab,\u00A0perhaps near the\u00A0Mars(or duna?) Pathfinder probe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nA simple sign saying \u0027Mark Watney(/Kerman?) woz ere\u0027 or similar.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-01T16:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeat idea! Could also be something simpler, like perhaps seeing a half buried \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E (from when before he got it in the rover)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-02T17:26:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA potato field.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpd.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd a bag of remained fertilizer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-02T17:27:28Z\u0022 title=\u002208/02/2019 05:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 2, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-03T21:15:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmake it subtler - a couple of spots where the ambient music changes to Kisco... (Kerbal Disco equivalent)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nK-M-C-A!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-04T03:41:58Z\u0022 title=\u002208/04/2019 03:41  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 4, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by zer0Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-04T14:27:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223644294\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564674061\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacenerd Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/1/2019 at 11:41 AM, Spacenerd Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, basically, an easter egg on Duna that\u0027d be referencing\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EThe Martian\u003C/em\u003E in some way. Comment what you think!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIdeas for the easter egg I\u0027ve had so far:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nMAV base\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHab somewhere on the ground\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe rover, complete with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E in the cab,\u00A0perhaps near the\u00A0Mars(or duna?) Pathfinder probe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nA simple sign saying \u0027Mark Watney(/Kerman?) woz ere\u0027 or similar.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nA wrecked habitat full of dead potatoes\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lithobrake","CreatedById":185579,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-04T17:29:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere are Some:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nThe junk he threw out of the Ares 4 MAV\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe MDV descent stage\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSome of the rocks he arranged in morse code messages\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAirlock one, on the ground\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe signs he used to communicate with JPL before he reprogrammed the rover\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nA sign half buried with a string attached that says \u0022ayyyyyyyyy\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-08T00:03:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223644294\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564674061\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022191542\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacenerd Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn \u200E8\u200E/\u200E1\u200E/\u200E2019 at 11:41 AM, Spacenerd Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, basically, an easter egg on Duna that\u0027d be referencing\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EThe Martian\u003C/em\u003E in some way. Comment what you think!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIdeas for the easter egg I\u0027ve had so far:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nMAV base\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHab somewhere on the ground\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe rover, complete with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E in the cab,\u00A0perhaps near the\u00A0Mars(or duna?) Pathfinder probe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nA simple sign saying \u0027Mark Watney(/Kerman?) woz ere\u0027 or similar.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMAV Base with the ability to go inside\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223647199\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565222590\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183218\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cheif Operations Director\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Cheif Operations Director said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMAV Base with the ability to go inside\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps an actual ship marked as debris\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"selfish_meme","CreatedById":125899,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-08T01:38:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPathfinder and Sojourner\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-08T14:46:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Kerbal body with \u0022Mark Watney\u0022 on suit.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-08T15:38:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA rover cabin with the note: \u0022To whom it may concern, take care of this Rover. She saved my life. Watney.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KeranoKerman","CreatedById":192437,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-08T22:48:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m thinking either a half buried \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003ERTG\u003C/abbr\u003E or an airlock 1 on the ground.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DRAG0Nmon","CreatedById":196609,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T01:37:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA sign that says:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u201DMark Kerman says ayyyyyyyyy\u201D\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsurrounded by potatoes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T07:36:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223648810\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565487439\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196609\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DRAG0Nmon\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, DRAG0Nmon said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsurrounded by potatoes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean blueberries? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T08:25:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA sudden sandstorm tearing your base apart in almost vacuum conditions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T09:15:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223647199\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565222590\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183218\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cheif Operations Director\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/8/2019 at 1:03 AM, Cheif Operations Director said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps an actual ship marked as debris\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt wouldnt be that fun to know from the traking station were it is\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T14:26:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223648909\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565514921\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbolExplorer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, KerbolExplorer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt wouldnt be that fun to know from the traking station were it is\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndebris are marked as turned off when the game first loads from the tracking station.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T14:46:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223648973\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565533594\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183218\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cheif Operations Director\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, Cheif Operations Director said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndebris are marked as turned off when the game first loads from the tracking station.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah but it would be as simple as turning it on and it will be inmidiatly found\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would like tho that the marker apeared once you discover the debris\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T15:18:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDerelict Hermes in solar orbit. They had spent all fuel by taking Watney from Mars. Now they are orbiting between Duna and Kerbin.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA crashed Mk1-3 pod with open nose and windows, no hatch, and a single command seat in the center.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt could be named \u0027Mk W\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-11T16:07:39Z\u0022 title=\u002208/11/2019 04:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 11, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by swjr-swis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-11T21:02:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223649014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221565539604\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA crashed Mk1-3 pod with open nose and windows, no hatch, and a single command seat in the center.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt could be named \u0027Mk W\u0027.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey should add all of this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Astrodym","CreatedById":190759,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt most it should be a half buried \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Radio-isotope Thermo-electric Generator (a.k.a. Mars rover heating device)\u0022\u003Ertg\u003C/abbr\u003E with the\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eayyy\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0sign and a hearth of snacks beneath. No potatos, just snacks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbMav","CreatedById":70338,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA loose antenna dish?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T05:34:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... and its stick stuck in Watney\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4472TJ","CreatedById":191771,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T11:28:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlthough I think this is a fantastic idea, it would be in a way promoting the Martian. (I sound like I don\u0027t want it, but I\u0027m trying to show the other side of the argument). I also feel that Easter eggs in KSP are normally related to real spaceflight endeavours that have changed the industry, or KSP related items, eg the Kracken. Although its a great idea its not real and I think Easter eggs should be reserved for only spectacular moments from spaceflight history.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T12:35:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA derelict ship with a mineralized Kerbal astronomer next to the telescope, and mysterious eggs spitting jumping krakenoids attaching to the helmet glass.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}